---
title: "Clinicians - Repurposed Research in Clinical Trials and Clinical Research"
description: "Use CureAccelerator to leverage repurposing research to be used in clinical trials and research."
---
<section role="banner" aria-label="repurposing-research" class="page-header header--green-alt">
  <div class="header-content__container role-page">
    <div class="header-content__left">
      <%= image_tag 'roles/clinician-img-2.png', alt: 'Clinicans', class: 'user-role-img' %>
    </div>
    <div class="header-content__right">
      <h6 class="title__inverse uppercase">Clinicians</h6>
      <h3 class="title__inverse">Why Join CureAccelerator?</h3>
      <p class="title__inverse">You are treating patients on a daily basis and are responsible for finding something that works for them. Share your knowledge of effective off-label use to drive future research, or follow the research here to find the newest treatment options for your patients.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Sign Up', ' https://app.cureaccelerator.org/registration', class: 'button button--white button--header' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= partial 'components/page-scroll' %>
</section>
<section class="callout--brown" role="region" aria-labelledby="about-cure-accelerator">
  <div class="callout--container">
    <blockquote class="text center">
      &quot;Deleloping new platforms that accelerate medical discovery is an important step in building a national Culture of Health where all people have access to the best possible care&quot;
      <cite>Deborah Bae, Senior Program Officer at the Robert Wood Johnson Foundation</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
<section role="region" aria-label="clinicians-features" id="page-scroll" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">What can I do with CureAccelerator?</h6>
  </header>
  <div class="page-section--body">
    <h1 class="title" id="clinicians-features">Contribute your knowledge of effective off-label use  to drive clinical care and research</h1>
    <p class="text">CureAccelerator’s community is composed of like-minded people who are dedicated to creating effective treatments through repurposing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid-layout">
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon share">Share</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Share observations off-label use</h5>
      <p>Your field experience could be the basis of the next new treatment. Start a discussion and share your observations today.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon peer">Colleagues</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Engage Your Clinical Colleagues</h5>
      <p>Help translate your pre-clinical findings into clinical trials.  Ask clinicians are your institution to join, or connect with clinicians on CureAccelerator who are already passionate about repurposing research.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon post">Post</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Post repurposing research ready for testing</h5>
      <p>Do you have an idea for a repurposed treatment ready for a clinical trial? We want to know about it, and so does the CureAccelerator funding community. Create a Project Proposal Summary today.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <i class="user-role-icon global-1">Global</i>
      <h5 class="grid-item--title">Join a global community</h5>
      <p>CureAccelerator is the world’s first online, interactive platform dedicated to repurposing research – a repurposing hub for people, knowledge and resources to connect in service to patients. Welcome!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<hr class="page-section--divider">
<section role="region" aria-labelledby="featured-users" class="page-section--container">
  <header role="section title" class="page-section--header">
    <div class="section-tag-border"></div>
    <h6 class="section--tag">CureAccelerator Community</h6>
  </header>
   <div class="page-section--body">
    <h2 class="title">Other User Roles</h2>
    <% link_to 'researchers.html', class: 'card one-half shift hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/researcher-img-2.png', alt: 'Researchers', class: 'card--border__green' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__green">Researchers</h5>
    <% end %>
    <% link_to 'funders.html', class: 'card one-half hover' do %>
      <%= image_tag 'roles/funders-img.png', alt: 'Funders', class: 'card--border__purple' %>
      <h5 class="card--title__purple">Funders</h5>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</section>